Extract Zarr data intersecting with vector polygons

Usage: eider extract [OPTIONS] <ZARR_URI> <VECTOR_PATH>

Arguments:
  <ZARR_URI>     The Zarr array URI
  <VECTOR_PATH>  Path to the vector boundaries (GeoJSON, Shapefile)

Options:
      --out <OUT>        Output DuckDB database file
  -y, --yes              Bypass confirmation prompts
      --pin <DIM=INDEX>  Pins for dimensions (e.g. --pin time=0)
      --output <OUTPUT>  Output format (table or json) [possible values: table, json]
  -h, --help             Print help
